FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS

Q: How do I start?
A: Create a character in the void (setter). Say help getting-started.

Q: How do I talk to other players?
A: say in a room, radio on your frequency, telepathy after introduce,
   tell for staff. See help communication.

Q: How do I get skills or spells?
A: Most come from your race and OCC at creation. Use improve to advance.

Q: How do I contact staff?
A: OOC channel or tell to an online wizard.

Q: Is ICQ still used?
A: No. ICQ was listed on the original website as a historical contact
   method. Use OOC or tell staff instead.

Q: Where is the old website help?
A: Type help or help <topic>. Many original index topics now have files here.

SEE ALSO: getting-started, communication, staff, riftsmud
